{
  "stem": "13096.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- I-- I-- I find a job, like a bookkeeper, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was trained.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] a bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the girls in the-- in the office, they become very friendly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were all Italian girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were about eight or 10.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They become very friendly with me, though, you know, they knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After a while, you know, because this office where I was working, it was Institute Nationale de [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a government-- a government office run, you know-- the men, you know, branch, it was in Rome.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they send a letter and they say, even in Rhodes Island, you are not allowed to employ Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when this order come to my branch in-- in Rhodes, the-- the-- the-- manager called me in his office and he told me, sorry.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Though we are very satisfied with your work, but we cannot keep you anymore in our-- in our office because you are Jewish-- you are a Jewish girl and we cannot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I have to leave, and I went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after a month or two, the girls where I was working with, they came to my house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were my friends, and they come and told me, you must come tomorrow to start work all over again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What's the outcome?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave an ultimatum, the 10 girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you are going to-- you are not going to take back Rachel, we are all to-- to give, you know, to have to resign.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All and they were all Italian girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
